------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 1.3.1
----------------------
CHANGES SINCE LAST TIME
    o A new citation is added.
    o Several bugs are corrected.

------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.17
----------------------
CHANGES SINCE LAST TIME
    o A new function, compareDMCs() is added for plotting DMCs and average predicted
    methylation for for group comparision.
    o The manhattanDMCs() function is modified to plot regions of interests.

------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.16
----------------------
CHANGES SINCE LAST TIME
    o The function findDMCs() is fixed for memory managment.
    o The function methEM() is fixed for creating NaN in computing binomial
    probabilities.

------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.15
----------------------
CHANGES SINCE LAST TIME
    o An option is added to findDMC that lets the user enters a function to
    calculate weights for GLM using the variances obtianed from MCMC.

------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.10 - 0.99.14
----------------------
CHANGES SINCE LAST TIME
    o Several issues are fixed.
    o Some modification are done to expedise the speed of processes.
    o Instead of the parallel package, the BioParallel package is used.

------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.9
----------------------
CHANGES SINCE LAST TIME
    o Some parameters in examples are changed to make the running time faster.
    o The BSData-method is changed to cBSData-method.
    o The BSDMCs-method is changed to cBSDMCs-method.

 BUG FIXES
    o None reported.


------------------------
CHANGES IN VERSION 0.99.0
----------------------
IMPROVEMENTS SINCE LAST TIME
    o We have refined some of the codes to speed up the running the package.

FUTURE DEVELOPMENT
    o Some functions will be rewitten in C.

BUG FIXES
    o None reported so far.
